        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/g/f08c70/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2017-11-03T23:47:47.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Not finding much information about the Beaune 1er Les Pertuisots that Sauzet is now making. I\u2019m assuming this is a relatively new addition to the Sauzet lineup. Anyone try this over the past few years? Is their commonality with their other wines in any way or is it a lone island? What\u2019s the history behind this red &amp; white vineyard\u2026is there anything remarkable or distinctive to this vineyard?  Thank you, Gary</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 10,
        "updated_at": "2022-06-03T01:32:45.597Z",
