        "created_at": "2017-11-04T00:22:15.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Jadot does this vineyard.  Only had the 2007 which is just ok but then I got a good deal on a case <span class=\"mention\">@25</span> per.  Never had the Sauzet, sorry.</p>",
