        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/g/f08c70/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2017-11-06T03:21:21.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Tom - Several years back 3 Sauzet siblings each received a 1/3 inheritance. One of the siblings decided to start their own business which brought the original Sauzet holdings down by that percentage. The business move has been to add back to reach original production.</p>",
